    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This R32 GT-R is a mechanically robust example of JDM engineering, powered by the iconic RB26DETT twin-turbocharged inline-six. The engine maintains strong compression across all cylinders and pulls cleanly through the rev range, with the ceramic turbos providing responsive boost. Power is managed by the sophisticated ATTESA E-TS all-wheel-drive system and a 5-speed manual gearbox with smooth gear synchronization. The chassis has been enhanced with adjustable dampers and aftermarket tension rods to sharpen turn-in response and mitigate understeer. Recent service includes a full fluid flush and timing belt replacement. The exterior presents well with minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with a well-maintained driver's car, while the interior remains largely stock, preserving the cockpit's ergonomic integrity.",
