      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2018 BMW 540i finished in a sophisticated Bluestone Metallic. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between executive luxury and athletic performance. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine runs flawlessly, providing the smooth, responsive power BMW is known for. The interior features premium black Dakota leather, a panoramic sunroof, and a high-definition iDrive navigation system. As a thorough seller, I want to note that the car is in great shape but shows minor signs of careful use: there is a small amount of curb rash on the rear passenger alloy wheel and light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All scheduled maintenance is current, including a recent synthetic oil change and a fresh set of Continental tires. The car has a clean title and has been smoke-free. This is a reliable, high-performing sedan that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 33900.0,
