      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a reliable companion. It is still in wonderful shape, runs super smooth, and has been very well-loved over the years! It\u2019s the perfect choice if you're looking for a dependable, great-looking car without that brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
